  "title": "Technical Engineer (Civil Engineering) #65005",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Technical Engineer</strong></li><li>Working Location: Boon Lay</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Mon – Fri, 9.00am – 6.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary up to $4,500 + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: 2-years Contract (Convertible to Permanent)</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare technical reports, design calculations, and specifications</li><li>Create 2D and 3D drawings as needed</li><li>Plan and oversee engineering projects</li><li>Conduct feasibility studies and technical assessments, including site investigations</li><li>Carry out site inspections and investigations as required</li><li>Coordinate and communicate with clients, authorities, architects, engineers, contractors, and suppliers to resolve design and development issues</li><li>Conduct research and gather data for projects and Capstone initiatives</li><li>Ensure project compliance with current codes of practice and legal requirements</li><li>Attend training courses provided by the company</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in civil & structural engineering, or relevant discipline</li><li>Recognised qualification by the Professional Engineers Board Singapore (PEB) preferred</li><li>Experience in restoration, civil or structural engineering design, or project management is an advantage</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office and engineering design software</li><li>Able to perform engineering hand calculations to relevant codes (BS/EC)</li><li>Experience with CAD or BIM is preferred</li><li>Willing to travel as required</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#65005 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
